      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEDERAL SAKI (6) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from five starts. Missed the frame latest (22.36) when fifth over 380m at this track in a Grade 5. Makes strong appeal on best. BEEP (3) broke from the inside draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 1.5 lengths (21.98) behind Ordinary at this track. Expected to feature. NO POWER (8) is a consistent type who is lining up for his first start here. Jumped well from box eight latest to win by a neck at Geelong (22.79) and has drawn the same this time. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Sure to be thereabouts. GIFTED JASPER (1) can fill a top-three spot.",
